snippet.description:
NO SCRIPT, NO FEAR, ALL OPINION
An off-the-cuff Video Blog about Electronics Engineering, for engineers, hobbyists, enthusiasts, hackers and Makers
Hosted by Dave Jones from Sydney Australia
